name: Solvaris Blueprint Chip
desc: The Blueprint Chip for Solvaris Remnants is a specialized enhancement designed to optimize the operational capabilities of solvaris missions. This chip incorporates advanced technologies and methodologies to support various objectives  particularly in improving efficiency and effectiveness ship.

name: Solvaris Blueprint Ship
desc: Enables heavy industry to construct ship hulls described by this blueprint.

name: Solvaris R&D
desc: This collection features a series of armory blueprints that elevate civilian spacecraft  specifically Solvaris models.

name: Exilium's Core
desc: The new beginning that the entire galaxy will acknowledge is Omega age during their peak time in this domain. a fresh start to tell the tale of how wonderful the world was before and after the fall of the homeworlds. On this core  we will revive the lost technology of the Omega's.
